UE5 Data Asset - DT_NPC_SpawnPool_NewAccra_v01
================================================

This is a Data Asset that contains spawn pool data for New Accra district.

To create this data asset in Unreal Engine 5.2+:
1. Right-click in Content Browser
2. Search for "Data Asset"
3. Select "DT_NPC_SpawnPool"
4. Click "Create"
5. Name it "DT_NPC_SpawnPool_NewAccra_v01"

Properties:
- SpawnPools (Array of FSpawnPoolData)
- KeyNPCNames (Array of FString)
- KeyNPCLocations (Map of FString to FVector)
- KeyNPCRotations (Map of FString to FRotator)

Spawn Pool Data:
- District: NewAccra
- RolePool: Citizen, Vendor, Government, CircleAgent
- NPCTypes: Array of NPC types
- SpawnPoints: Array of spawn locations
- MaxPopulation: 100
- SpawnRate: 60.0f
- Time Filters: Morning, Afternoon, Evening, Night

Key NPCs:
- AuntieEfua (Vendor)
- BabaHassan (Government)
- Kwame (GangMember)

Note: This data asset must be configured by designers.
Note: This data asset requires spawn points from level designers.
Note: This data asset requires persistent NPC locations from designers.